FROM title t, cast_info ci, movie_keyword mk
WHERE t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.kind_id  =  7 AND t.production_year  <  2005 AND ci.person_id  >  3180518 AND mk.keyword_id  =  348
